main event: A civilian observed a bright greenish object in the sky for several minutes, initially believed to be a UFO, later concluded to be Venus.
interesting points: The object remained stationary for several minutes., The observer reported the object as bright and greenish-colored., The observation was made in clear weather conditions., The witness had prior experience with similar sightings., The conclusion of the report identified the object as Venus.
witness description: Mr. Rodgers, age 25, male, prior UFO sightings
